Selector parsers.

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AttributeSelectorParser
    Parses an AttributeSelector.
    ClassSelectorParser
    Parses a ClassSelector.
    CombinatorParser
    Parses Combinators.
    ComplexSelectorParser
    Parses refined Selectors, as opposed to SelectorParser.
    IdSelectorParser
    Parses an IdSelector.
    PseudoSelectorParser
    Parses both PseudoClassSelectors and PseudoElementSelectors.
    SelectorParser
    Parses a Selector.

    Parses a sequence of comma-separated selectors.
    TypeSelectorParser
